  "title": "Sunshake!",
  "description": "Turns Cows into Wocs from Scrap Mechanic!",
  "body": "<center>\n  <h1>\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/cb6217f9ad1fcdfb9ac06ccce09fe9b3727e9b5b.png\" alt=\"Sunshake!\">\n  </h1>\n  <p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/sunshake/\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8a2dd1324a19f7594a6e032659b78fb3e5e89a2d.png\" alt=\"Modrinth\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/sunshake/\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/48f3ed3f11e619ef7fea93c4344ae8f4ba233cb0.png\" alt=\"Planet Minecraft\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/p4ncake\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1fab8f2e1518ab9f6373586085d9aa785e0e3b9d.png\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-Fi\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/C9Q6XFG8T8\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6f5a8b8552da877af71a331499e3fffcb57b513a.png\" alt=\"Join our Community on Discord!\"></a></p>\n  <hr>\n  <p><b>Sunshake!</b> is a 16x16 Resourcepack inspired by the game Scrap Mechanic. Optifine/Emf recommended. For now it only replaces the Cow with the <a href=\"https://scrapmechanic.fandom.com/wiki/Woc\">Scrap Mechanic Woc</a>, but who knows what this project could become in the future :3</p>\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/35af6a93e948f256e22005934106adf6026869d1.jpeg\" alt=\"A majestic screenshot of a Woc staring into the sunlight\">\n  <p><br>If you want to get notified for updates on the pack progress, give me suggestions or you wanna report any bugs, consider joining my Discord server <a href=\"https://discord.gg/C9Q6XFG8T8\">here</a>!</p>\n</center>",
